page.title: 14GARAGES IN WELLS, NORFOLK
page.content: There are six garages in Wells including Roses, Popes, Barkers, Walsinghams, Orchard Caravan and Coronation Garages. Although Wells is a small place there are quite a lot of garages. My Mum and Dad own Coronation Garage where my Dad is the Chief Mechanic and my Mum does the paperwork, serves petrol and other odd jobs like that. They employ two men to work for them. Coronation Garage is near the edge of town on the main coast road so we are quite busy as people coming in and out of Wells usually come to us.
